# MDM 控制中台 - 功能逻辑对齐表
# 由 agentcp 生成

## 模块一：设备资产与生命周期管理

### 1.1 设备注册接口
```json
{
  "module": "device_asset",
  "feature": "设备注册",
  "endpoint": "/api/v1/devices/register",
  "method": "POST",
  "description": "新设备首次连网上报身份，完成注册",
  "request": {
    "device_id": "string (UUID, 必填)",
    "mac_address": "string (MAC地址, 必填)",
    "sn_code": "string (序列号, 必填)",
    "hardware_model": "string (硬件型号, 必填)",
    "firmware_version": "string (固件版本, 必填)"
  },
  "response": {
    "success": {
      "status": 200,
      "body": {
        "device_id": "string",
        "lifecycle_status": 1,
        "message": "设备注册成功"
      }
    },
    "error": {
      "status": 400,
      "body": {
        "error_code": "ERR_DEVICE_001",
        "message": "设备ID或MAC地址已存在"
      }
    }
  },
  "precondition": "设备必须首次联网，未在系统中存在",
  "business_logic": "校验UUID和MAC唯一性 -> 插入设备记录 -> 状态置为待激活(1)"
}
```

### 1.2 用户绑定接口
```json
{
  "module": "device_asset",
  "feature": "用户扫码绑定",
  "endpoint": "/api/v1/devices/{sn_code}/bind",
  "method": "POST",
  "description": "用户扫码绑定设备",
  "request": {
    "bind_user_id": "string (用户ID, 必填)"
  },
  "response": {
    "success": {
      "status": 200,
      "body": {
        "device_id": "string",
        "bind_user_id": "string",
        "lifecycle_status": 2,
        "message": "绑定成功"
      }
    }
  },
  "precondition": "设备sn_code存在且lifecycle_status为1或2",
  "business_logic": "校验sn_code -> 更新bind_user_id -> 状态改为服役中(2) -> 触发OpenClaw初始化"
}
```

## 模块二：设备影子与状态监控

### 2.1 心跳上报接口
```json
{
  "module": "device_shadow",
  "feature": "设备心跳上报",
  "endpoint": "/api/v1/devices/{device_id}/heartbeat",
  "method": "POST",
  "description": "设备定期上报状态",
  "request": {
    "connection_status": "enum [online, offline, poor_network]",
    "battery_level": "int (0-100)",
    "charging_status": "boolean",
    "current_mode": "enum [sleeping, roaming, listening, talking, idle]",
    "rssi": "int"
  },
  "response": {
    "success": {
      "status": 200,
      "body": {
        "received": true,
        "server_time": "ISO8601"
      }
    }
  },
  "precondition": "设备已注册且已绑定用户",
  "business_logic": "更新Redis缓存 -> 更新PostgreSQL影子表 -> 检查离线超时(90秒)"
}
```

### 2.2 状态查询接口
```json
{
  "module": "device_shadow",
  "feature": "查询设备状态",
  "endpoint": "/api/v1/devices/{device_id}/status",
  "method": "GET",
  "description": "OpenClaw查询设备当前状态",
  "response": {
    "status": 200,
    "body": {
      "device_id": "string",
      "is_online": "boolean",
      "battery_level": "int",
      "current_mode": "string",
      "last_heartbeat": "ISO8601",
      "desired_config": "JSON"
    }
  },
  "precondition": "设备已注册",
  "business_logic": "从Redis查询 -> 无则查PostgreSQL -> 返回JSON"
}
```

